span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja-JP">雛のように産まれ丶幾年も非力で生さるため 泣さつく</span></p><p begin="28.570" end="32.530" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="28.570" end="28.900">衰</span><span begin="28.900" end="29.150">老</span><span begin="29.150" end="29.400">之</span><span begin="29.400" end="29.700">后</span><span begin="29.700" end="29.970">被</span><span begin="29.970" end="30.660">病</span><span begin="30.750" end="31.430">痛</span><span begin="31.430" end="32.060">缠</span><span begin="32.060" end="32.530">住</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en-US">Age brings nothing but pain to bear</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja-JP">老いては病に蝕まれる</span></p><p begin="32.840" end="40.980" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="32.840" end="33.100">剩</span><span begin="33.100" end="33.460">下</span><span begin="33.460" end="33.630">人</span><span begin="33.630" end="33.940">生</span><span begin="33.940" end="34.220">中</span><span begin="34.220" end="35.080">段</span><span begin="35.080" end="35.660">无</span><span begin="35.660" end="36.420">效</span><span begin="36.420" end="37.180">劳</span><span begin="37.180" end="38.040">苦</span> <span begin="38.540" end="38.980">养</span><span begin="38.980" end="39.330">其</span><span begin="39.330" end="39.860">他</span><span begin="39.860" end="40.400">废</span><span begin="40.400" end="40.980">物</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en-US">Middle years spent in futile toil, raising more wasteful lives in soil</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja-JP">それ以外の人生(とさ)も無意味に苦労され さらに自分のような廃物を育て</span></p><p begin="41.480" end="45.380" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="41.480" end="41.740">挣</span><span begin="41.740" end="42.010">扎</span><span begin="42.010" end="42.230">在</span><span begin="42.230" end="42.530">进</span><span begin="42.530" end="42.720">化</span><span begin="42.720" end="43.670">树</span><span begin="43.670" end="44.460">的</span><span begin="44.460" end="44.690">低</span><span begin="44.690" end="45.380">处</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en-US">Stagnating on evolution&apos;s lowest rung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja-JP">進化樹の根っこんでたじろいと足掻いている</span></p><p begin="45.750" end="49.730" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="45.750" end="46.030">还</span><span begin="46.030" end="46.280">放</span><span begin="46.280" end="46.480">任</span><span begin="46.480" end="46.770">情</span><span begin="46.770" end="47.020">绪</span><span begin="47.020" end="47.900">分</span><span begin="47.900" end="48.620">泌</span><span begin="48.620" end="49.200">过</span><span begin="49.200" end="49.730">度</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en-US">By emotional impulses repeatedly stung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja-JP">己の情緒を無駄に垂らして</span></p><p begin="50.060" end="58.600" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="50.060" end="50.190">无</span><span begin="50.190" end="50.550">限</span><span begin="50.550" end="50.840">放</span><span begin="50.840" end="51.040">大</span><span begin="51.040" end="51.250">自</span><span begin="51.250" end="52.070">身</span><span begin="52.070" end="53.000">狭</span><span begin="53.000" end="53.520">隘</span><span begin="53.520" end="54.300">好</span><span begin="54.300" end="55.210">恶</span> <span begin="55.700" end="56.010">爆</span><span begin="56.010" end="56.260">发</span><span begin="56.260" end="57.060">笑</span><span begin="57.280" end="57.880">或</span><span begin="57.880" end="58.600">哭</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en-US">Magnifying your narrow views, between laughter and tears you can&apos;t choose</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja-JP">偏狭な好悪を無限して広げ 大いに笑うと泣くことを繰りかえす</span></p><p begin="1:00.780" end="1:09.070" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:00.780" end="1:00.980">无</span><span begin="1:00.980" end="1:01.180">知</span><span begin="1:01.180" end="1:01.490">是</span><span begin="1:01.490" end="1:01.810">福</span> <span begin="1:01.810" end="1:02.090">一</span><span begin="1:02.090" end="1:03.060">叶</span><span begin="1:03.630" end="1:04.250">障</span><span begin="1:04.250" end="1:04.810">目</span> <span begin="1:05.330" end="1:05.780">眼</span><span begin="1:05.780" end="1:06.340">前</span><span begin="1:06.340" end="1:07.020">就</span><span begin="1:07.020" end="1:07.660">是</span><span begin="1:07.660" end="1:08.570">全</span><span begin="1:08.570" end="1:09.070">部</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en-US">Ignorance is bliss, blinded by a single leaf; what&apos;s in front of you is all you see</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja-JP">無知はお前らの至福 一葉で目を蔽う 見生が全てだと思えて</span></p><p begin="1:09.510" end="1:17.550" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:09.510" end="1:10.050">七</span><span begin="1:10.050" end="1:10.620">情</span><span begin="1:10.620" end="1:11.430">六</span><span begin="1:11.430" end="1:11.810">欲</span><span begin="1:12.150" end="1:12.480">来</span><span begin="1:12.480" end="1:12.700">回</span><span begin="1:12.700" end="1:13.550">虚</span><span begin="1:13.550" end="1:14.060">度</span> <span begin="1:14.420" end="1:14.940">又</span><span begin="1:14.940" end="1:15.480">带</span><span begin="1:15.480" end="1:15.710">不</span><span begin="1:15.710" end="1:16.450">进</span><span begin="1:16.560" end="1:17.070">坟</span><span begin="1:17.070" end="1:17.550">墓</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en-US">Wasting time on feelings deep, none of which you get to keep</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja-JP">諸々の情欲に虚しく振り回される 墓場に持ち込めずと知りながらも</span></p><p begin="1:17.910" end="1:26.170" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:17.910" end="1:18.170">可</span><span begin="1:18.170" end="1:18.370">每</span><span begin="1:18.370" end="1:18.700">只</span><span begin="1:18.700" end="1:18.900">不</span><span begin="1:18.900" end="1:19.220">起</span><span begin="1:19.220" end="1:20.570">眼</span><span begin="1:20.830" end="1:21.289">的</span><span begin="1:21.289" end="1:21.940">虫</span> <span begin="1:22.380" end="1:22.960">仍</span><span begin="1:22.960" end="1:23.470">执</span><span begin="1:23.470" end="1:24.890">着</span><span begin="1:24.890" end="1:25.690">心</span><span begin="1:25.690" end="1:26.170">动</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en-US">Yet each insignificant being persists in feeling, dreaming, seeing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja-JP">虫螻のお前らは 僅かに感じる鼓動に執着している</span></p><p begin="1:26.630" end="1:36.240" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:26.630" end="1:27.270">命</span><span begin="1:27.270" end="1:27.720">如</span><span begin="1:27.720" end="1:28.560">草</span><span begin="1:28.560" end="1:29.000">芥</span> <span begin="1:29.370" end="1:29.660">弱</span><span begin="1:29.660" end="1:29.900">不</span><span begin="1:29.900" end="1:30.690">禁</span><span begin="1:30.690" end="1:31.240">风</span> <span begin="1:31.490" end="1:31.990">却</span><span begin="1:31.990" end="1:32.530">相</span><span begin="1:32.530" end="1:32.800">互</span><span begin="1:32.800" end="1:33.240">承</span><span begin="1:33.240" end="1:33.690">诺</span><span begin="1:33.690" end="1:34.250">永</span><span begin="1:34.250" end="1:36.240">恒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en-US">Fragile as grass in the wind. Still promising forever, twinned</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja-JP">風さえ耐えられぬ 脆く丶儚さ ちりあくたの分際で 永遠を約束はようとする</span></p><p begin="1:36.930" end="1:45.900" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:36.930" end="1:37.370">无</span><span begin="1:37.370" end="1:37.950">情</span><span begin="1:37.950" end="1:38.430">宇</span><span begin="1:38.430" end="1:39.320">宙</span><span begin="1:39.320" end="1:39.840">中</span> <span begin="1:40.150" end="1:40.610">唯</span><span begin="1:40.610" end="1:41.450">一</span><span begin="1:41.450" end="1:41.979">敢</span><span begin="1:42.190" end="1:42.720">深</span><span begin="1:42.720" end="1:43.640">情</span><span begin="1:43.640" end="1:44.340">的</span><span begin="1:44.340" end="1:44.920">物</span><span begin="1:44.920" end="1:45.900">种</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en-US">In this indifferent universe, only you dare to love so deep</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja-JP">非情なこ宇宙で 情深を唯一な群(ヤッら)よ</span></p><p begin="1:46.570" end="1:54.030" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:46.570" end="1:47.000">多</span><span begin="1:47.000" end="1:47.920">稚</span><span begin="1:47.920" end="1:48.430">嫩</span> <span begin="1:48.720" end="1:49.140">多</span><span begin="1:49.140" end="1:50.009">放</span><span begin="1:50.009" end="1:50.550">纵</span> <span begin="1:50.830" end="1:51.350">爱</span><span begin="1:51.350" end="1:52.160">恨</span><span begin="1:52.160" end="1:52.590">如</span><span begin="1:52.590" end="1:53.220">泉</span><span begin="1:53.220" end="1:54.030">涌</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en-US">How naive, how rash, with passions you leap</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja-JP">幼稚で丶無謀にも 愛憎は泉の如くに湧さやめず</span></p><p begin="1:54.330" end="2:02.660" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:54.330" end="1:54.570">你</span><span begin="1:54.570" end="1:54.850">们</span><span begin="1:54.850" end="1:55.130">永</span><span begin="1:55.130" end="1:55.390">不</span><span begin="1:55.390" end="1:55.600">懂</span> <span begin="1:55.600" end="1:56.460">亲</span><span begin="1:56.460" end="1:56.940">吻</span><span begin="1:57.250" end="1:57.670">和</span><span begin="1:57.670" end="1:58.550">相</span><span begin="1:58.550" end="1:59.020">拥</span><span begin="1:59.420" end="1:59.930">都</span><span begin="1:59.930" end="2:00.760">百</span><span begin="2:00.760" end="2:01.250">无</span><span begin="2:01.250" end="2:01.850">一</span><span begin="2:01.850" end="2:02.660">用</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en-US">You&apos;ll never understand that kisses and embraces mean nothing in the cosmic plan</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja-JP">お前らは決してわからないのであろう キスと抱擁は全くにもって意味ない</span></p><p begin="2:02.870" end="2:13.160" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:02.870" end="2:03.150">头</span><span begin="2:03.150" end="2:03.420">顶</span><span begin="2:03.420" end="2:03.680">这</span><span begin="2:03.680" end="2:04.160">片</span><span begin="2:04.160" end="2:05.060">星</span><span begin="2:05.060" end="2:05.540">空</span> <span begin="2:05.860" end="2:06.380">对</span><span begin="2:06.380" end="2:07.150">人</span><span begin="2:07.150" end="2:07.650">间</span><span begin="2:07.880" end="2:08.259">向</span><span begin="2:08.259" end="2:08.520">来</span><span begin="2:08.520" end="2:09.320">无</span><span begin="2:09.320" end="2:10.090">动</span><span begin="2:10.090" end="2:10.660">于</span><span begin="2:10.660" end="2:13.160">衷</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en-US">These stars above your head to human affairs remain cold and dead</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja-JP">見上げたこの空は 君ら人門にいささかも見向さもしないのだ</span></p><p begin="2:30.750" end="2:39.070" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:30.750" end="2:30.920">可</span><span begin="2:30.920" end="2:31.230">每</span><span begin="2:31.230" end="2:31.530">只</span><span begin="2:31.530" end="2:31.880">无</span><span begin="2:31.880" end="2:32.130">意</span><span begin="2:32.130" end="2:33.570">义</span><span begin="2:33.710" end="2:34.180">的</span><span begin="2:34.180" end="2:34.890">虫</span> <span begin="2:35.270" end="2:35.790">梦</span><span begin="2:35.790" end="2:36.390">想</span><span begin="2:36.390" end="2:37.160">都</span><span begin="2:37.160" end="2:37.490">不</span><span begin="2:37.490" end="2:38.500">相</span><span begin="2:38.500" end="2:39.070">同</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en-US">Yet each meaningless creature here, dreams different dreams year after year</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja-JP">虫螻のお前らはまた それぞれの夢を見ている</span></p><p begin="2:39.570" end="2:47.660" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2: